Wisconsin ili Bugtussle,
Tennessee...

153
00:07:41,810 --> 00:07:43,878
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">...to je, to je jedan od njihovih.</font>

154
00:07:44,012 --> 00:07:44,745
u redu

155
